title: 'Good product'
body: 'Product is very good. Not sure whether you will get this quality material if purchased in local stores. Also not sure what the price would be.  Found pockets inside and outside for wearing the coat in the reverse way.  But here is the other face of this brand. They are promising cashbacks / freebies for rating / reviews in online store. Obviously people will provide good ratings for their promised freebies.  So not sure how many these ratings are genuine. For every product there will be both good / bad and avg reviews.. whereas here because of instant cashbacks / freebies u will find only 5 stars max.  Fyi for my review they gave 25% off on worthless items :-P'

title: 'Met all expectations. Without thinking
body: '4.0 out of 5 stars'It has all spec that I needed for long raincoat. Hood is well fit with tie lock. Zipper is smooth with buttons, giving dual protection.
